            house: "Baratheon"
            religion: "Faith of the Seven"
        notes: "Officially the eldest son of Robert I Baratheon and Cersei Lannister. Actually the product of Cersei's incestuous relationship with Jaime Lannister. Golden-haired, green-eyed. Cruel, cowardly, and capricious. Ordered the execution of Eddard Stark against his council's wishes. Died at the Purple Wedding — his marriage feast with Margaery Tyrell — poisoned by the Strangler in his wine, a plot by Olenna Tyrell and Petyr Baelish."
